<div1 type="trialAccount" id="t17511204-1">
               <interp inst="t17511204-1" type="collection" value="BAILEY"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17511204-1" type="year" value="1751"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17511204-1" type="uri" value="sessionsPapers/17511204"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17511204-1" type="date" value="17511204"></interp>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17511204-1-off1-c30" targOrder="Y" targets="t17511204-1-defend31 t17511204-1-off1 t17511204-1-verdict4"></join>
         
               <p>1. (L.) 
               
                  <persName id="t17511204-1-defend31" type="defendantName">
                     John 
                     Felton 
                  <interp inst="t17511204-1-defend31" type="surname" value="Felton"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17511204-1-defend31" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17511204-1-defend31" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , was indicted for <rs id="t17511204-1-off1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17511204-1-off1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17511204-1-off1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pettyLarceny"></interp>
               stealing one linen handkerchief, value 10 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17511204-1-victim33" type="victimName">
                     George 
                     Clark 
                  <interp inst="t17511204-1-victim33" type="surname" value="Clark"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17511204-1-victim33" type="given" value="George"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17511204-1-victim33" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17511204-1-off1 t17511204-1-victim33"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17511204-1-cd2" type="crimeDate">Oct. 24</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17511204-1-off1 t17511204-1-cd2"></join>. ++.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17511204-1-person34">
                  George 
                  Clark 
               <interp inst="t17511204-1-person34" type="surname" value="Clark"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17511204-1-person34" type="given" value="George"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17511204-1-person34" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the twenty-fourth of October, between twelve and one at noon, there was a-stop occasioned by a coach at the <placeName id="t17511204-1-crimeloc3">end of Birchin-lane, Lombard-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17511204-1-crimeloc3" type="placeName" value="end of Birchin-lane, Lombard-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17511204-1-crimeloc3" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17511204-1-off1 t17511204-1-crimeloc3"></join>; standing there I thought I felt something in my pocket, I turned about and saw the prisoner with my handkerchief in his hand, he seeing me look at him let it fall, I took hold on him, and took up the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>Q. When had you seen your handkerchief last before that?</p>
               <p>Clark. I had made use of it but a little time before; the prisoner said it was not him, it was another boy; but there were none near him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>There was a great mob at the corner of the street, and many other people besides me.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17511204-1-verdict4" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17511204-1-verdict4" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17511204-1-punish5" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17511204-1-punish5" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17511204-1-defend31 t17511204-1-punish5"></join>
               
                     <note>[Transportation. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
            </div1>
